@chapter{ Environment }

@a{environ}
The following environment variables are recognized by Doomsday.

@deflist{

@item{DOOMWADDIR} DOOM WAD directory. Doomsday looks for WAD files in this
directory.

@item{DOOMWADPATH} Delimited set of DOOM WAD directories. Use @ifdef{WIN32}{semicolon (;)}@else{colon (:)} to separate directories. Supported WAD files are searched for in each directory.

}
